1)compatiable version download for hase-hadoop  (Take hbase-0.90.6 version)
2)Copy hadoop-core*.jar, common-configuration*.jar, common-collection*.jar  from hadoop ---> hbase/lib/ 
3) Copy hdfs-site.xml from hadoop/conf/ ---> hbase/conf/
4) Configure hbase-site.xml accordingly
5) comment if there is any 127.0.1.1 in /etc/hosts